===message:You have some good points and I agree with them.  Although the British government may have thought it was reasonable that the American colonies help with the national debt, they failed to realized that laws and policies are to benefit all citizens.  The colonies soon realized that the British government policies were wrong and burdensome, which eventually lead to the colonies requesting separation.
